data.description: Welcome to this two-story all brick beauty, featuring 4 spacious bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms for comfortable living. Cozy up in the family room by the fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings. The formal dining room flows seamlessly into the spacious living room, ideal for entertaining. The kitchen boasts custom oak cabinets and ample amount of countertops including a built-in desk. Cedar hall closet and lots of storage in full size basement. Descend into the basement for a luxurious sauna experience and separate shower. Outside, the large gated backyard offers a tranquil koi pond and wooded surroundings. This property promises both space, serenity and much more. Call today to schedule your appointmenat and ask me about how you may quilifiy up to $7500k grant.
